Configuration For RainLoop Development in Ubuntu 14.04

1.clone repo in github

2.install noude_modules for gulp building

3.modify "navbar.less" at line 188 as follows:
width: (@gridColumnWidth * @gridColumns) + (@gridGutterWidth * (@gridColumns - 1));
//  #grid > .core > .span(@gridColumns);

4.in the repo directory gulp build
gulp

5.visit rainloop in localhost browse.